# Adding Trivia Questions — TRIVIA.md

How to add new club history trivia questions to the game.

---

## Trivia JSON Schema

All questions live in `/src/data/trivia.json`:

```json
{
  "id": "unique_question_id",
  "sport": "football | orienteering | petanque | running | biking | rowing | general",
  "era": "early | middle | recent",
  "question": {
    "en": "Question text in English?",
    "fi": "Kysymys suomeksi?"
  },
  "answers": {
    "en": ["Correct Answer", "Wrong Answer 1", "Wrong Answer 2", "Wrong Answer 3"],
    "fi": ["Oikea vastaus", "Väärä vastaus 1", "Väärä vastaus 2", "Väärä vastaus 3"]
  },
  "correctIndex": 0
}
```

The `correctIndex` is always 0 in the source file. The game shuffles the answers before displaying.

---

## Era Guide

| Era | Approximate Years |
|-----|------------------|
| `early` | 2005–2010 |
| `middle` | 2011–2017 |
| `recent` | 2018–2025 |

---

## Tips for Good Questions

- The best questions are ones only the crew would know
- Specific moments beat general knowledge (who scored vs what year founded)
- Embarrassing moments make for the best wrong answers
- Keep answers roughly similar length so the correct one doesn't stand out

---

## Example Questions

```json
[
  {
    "id": "first_goal_ever",
    "sport": "football",
    "era": "early",
    "question": {
      "en": "Who scored the very first goal in Olvastin Tana history?",
      "fi": "Kuka teki Olvastin Tanan historian ensimmäisen maalin?"
    },
    "answers": {
      "en": ["Mattila", "Alanen", "Mauno", "Mehtonen"],
      "fi": ["Mattila", "Alanen", "Mauno", "Mehtonen"]
    },
    "correctIndex": 0
  },
  {
    "id": "petanque_champion",
    "sport": "petanque",
    "era": "middle",
    "question": {
      "en": "Who won the first official Olvastin Tana petanque championship?",
      "fi": "Kuka voitti ensimmäisen virallisen Olvastin Tanan petanque-mestaruuden?"
    },
    "answers": {
      "en": ["Player A", "Player B", "Player C", "Player D"],
      "fi": ["Pelaaja A", "Pelaaja B", "Pelaaja C", "Pelaaja D"]
    },
    "correctIndex": 0
  }
]
```

---

## Checklist When Adding Questions

- [ ] Add to `/src/data/trivia.json`
- [ ] `id` is unique
- [ ] Both `en` and `fi` versions filled in for question AND all answers
- [ ] `correctIndex` is set to 0 (game will shuffle)
- [ ] `sport` tag is one of the valid values
- [ ] `era` tag is set correctly
